      <title>解释者：中国在风力涡轮机制造领域的主导地位</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-dominance-wind-turbine-manufacturing-2024-04-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟反垄断专员玛格丽特·维斯塔格(Margrethe Vestager)表示，欧盟将调查中国输往欧洲的风力涡轮机供应商收到的补贴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-dominance-wind-turbine-manufacturing-2024-04-10/</guid>
