    <item>
      <title>商会称大多数德国企业认为在中国存在不公平竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/majority-german-firms-feel-unfair-competition-china-commerce-chamber-says-2024-04-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国德国商会周三进行的一项调查显示，近三分之二的德国企业认为，他们在中国遇到了来自当地企业的不公平竞争，并且在接触当地官员、信息和许可方面处于劣势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/majority-german-firms-feel-unfair-competition-china-commerce-chamber-says-2024-04-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:07:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>向中国发出工厂产能警告后，耶伦面临关税决定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/after-issuing-factory-capacity-warning-china-yellen-faces-tariff-decisions-2024-04-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦在对广州和北京进行为期四天的访问期间，向中国经济领导人发出严厉警告，称他们对清洁能源产品工厂产能的过度投资是不可接受的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/after-issuing-factory-capacity-warning-china-yellen-faces-tariff-decisions-2024-04-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 05:05:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾总统表示与美国和日本的峰会将包括南海合作</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-president-says-trilateral-summit-with-us-japan-include-south-china-2024-04-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周三表示，即将举行的美国、菲律宾和日本三边峰会将包括一项维护南海安全和航行自由的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-president-says-trilateral-summit-with-us-japan-include-south-china-2024-04-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 04:05:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿里巴巴马云从阴影中走出来，发表鼓舞士气的帖子</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-founder-jack-ma-steps-out-shadows-with-long-internal-post-2024-04-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿里巴巴联合创始人马云向员工写了一份冗长的备忘录，表达了对这家互联网巨头重组工作的支持，这是这位亿万富翁在过去几年远离聚光灯后的罕见举动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-founder-jack-ma-steps-out-shadows-with-long-internal-post-2024-04-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 04:03:17 GMT</pubDate>
